Comment: 10,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You stingy dragon!
Comment: 10,0:18:37.47,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You return what you borrow. That's how the real world works.
Comment: 10,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking everything that you owe me!
Comment: 10,0:18:44.64,0:18:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe you exactly nothing.
Comment: 10,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Comment: 10,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Comment: 10,0:18:50.31,0:18:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the promissory note you signed with Luna Nova one thousand years ago.
Comment: 10,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Promissory note"?
Comment: 10,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a promissory note?
Comment: 10,0:18:58.61,0:19:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's written in ancient Dragonese, so nobody could read it. {sounds good to me, or we could use Old[e] Dragonese}{## this should be good, makes most sense linguistically; i was thinking of Dragontongue but we shouldn't inject too much}{BD: someone was all like this should be "Draconic", but it doesn't matter}
Comment: 10,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can, Diana?
Comment: 10,0:19:04.79,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I became fluent at the age of twelve.
Comment: 10,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no mention of interest anywhere on this.
Comment: 10,0:19:10.75,0:19:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means there was never a need to pay interest in the first place.
Comment: 10,0:19:14.46,0:19:20.43,Default,,15,15,0,,You abused the fact that our teachers could not read ancient Dragonese and pulled the wool over their eyes!
Comment: 10,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You had them pay nonexistent interest!{## they did pay interest in the past?}
Comment: 10,0:19:31.23,0:19:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A baseless accusation. There's no such thing\Nas a non-interest-bearing loan these days.{## let's go full technical}
Comment: 10,0:19:35.27,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I declare a contract that old invalid!
Comment: 10,0:19:39.07,0:19:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are we to understand that the debt itself is also invalidated?
Comment: 10,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's—
Comment: 10,0:19:45.24,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the sum of the payments made by Luna Nova far exceeds the principal sum of the initial debt.{## this should be fully correct without going over the top with technicalities, also "amount of capital" does not apply here; tfw writing a final thesis in a finance topic}{just you wait, one day we'll sub an anime about neuroscience}
Comment: 10,0:19:50.79,0:19:58.09,Default,,15,15,0,,Considering that the interest itself has been invalidated,\Nmay we assume the rest of the debt to be cleared?
Comment: 10,0:19:58.42,0:20:03.89,Default,,15,15,0,,Regarding the refunding of the overpayments, we will provide you with the proper documentation at a later date.
Comment: 10,0:20:07.06,0:20:14.02,Default,,15,15,0,,In light of these arguments, we request the immediate return of our Sorcerer's Stone, {\fax-0.2}Mister{\i0} Fafnir.{## wanna italicize the "mister" to make it clear she's on the same level as him, unlike the headmistress?; good mic drop opportunity}{sure why not}
Comment: 10,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Comment: 10,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was the end...
Comment: 10,0:20:24.61,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The world has no need for dragons or witches in this age of science.
Comment: 10,0:20:30.20,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is fated to be forgotten in the near future.
Comment: 10,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't happen!
Comment: 10,0:20:36.46,0:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, magic has the power to move hearts!
Comment: 10,0:20:41.30,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been quite some time since I've last heard someone spout a line that naive.
Comment: 10,0:20:46.55,0:20:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch! I'm gonna become an amazing witch one day and make the whole world gasp in surprise!
Comment: 10,0:20:52.06,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Is that the dream you were talking about?
Comment: 10,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Comment: 10,0:21:02.74,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll learn soon enough that no man can live off dreams alone.
Comment: 10,0:21:07.95,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Gramps! Try and keep your greed in check.
Comment: 10,0:21:26.09,0:21:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that there were still humans\Nwith that look in their eyes.
Comment: 10,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the end, we're back to laundry duty.
Comment: 10,0:21:44.53,0:21:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you expect? We broke the rules\Nand left campus without permission.
Comment: 10,0:21:49.03,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Be grateful this is the end of our punishment.
Comment: 10,0:21:52.04,0:21:57.29,Default,,15,15,0,,Yeah, but it still sucks that Diana totally stole the show.
Comment: 10,0:21:57.29,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me.
Comment: 10,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how perfect can one girl be?
Comment: 10,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so perfect I wanna hurl.
Comment: 10,0:22:04.63,0:22:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what makes her worth taking down!
Comment: 10,0:22:07.34,0:22:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no qualms with her as my rival.
Comment: 10,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You're nowhere near good enough for that.
Comment: 10,0:22:12.76,0:22:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember your place as the school's biggest dunce.
Comment: 10,0:22:18.98,0:22:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest dunce here is{\fax-0.2} you{\i0}, Amanda!{## heh, for good measure}
Comment: 10,0:22:21.98,0:22:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\fax-0.2}you{\i0}, Akko!
Comment: 10,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again!
Comment: 10,0:22:24.90,0:22:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Comment: 10,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just stop it already, you two!
Comment: 10,0:02:58.78,0:02:59.78,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,1027.5)}It's you!
Comment: 10,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.24,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,According to my calculations,
Comment: 10,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.94,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,We're saved...
